name: SAP-ERP-Fraud-Data
description: This repository provides additional information and data on the paper "Analyzing Data Sets for ML-driven Fraud Detection in SAP Systems" by Schnepf et al.

name: data-lineage-analyzer
description: This project provides a framework for analyzing data lineage and the impact of changes in source columns using DBT and DuckDB. It allows users to trace data flows through various stages and visualize the effects of column changes on downstream tables.

name: Segy
description: Classes and functions for reading SEGY files.

name: ResSched
description: A resource-aware scheduler for distributed deep learning workloads.

name: url-shortener
description: A scalable, multi-tenant URL shortening service built with NX and NestJS, designed as a collection of microservices and deployed on Kubernetes. This service provides URL shortening capabilities with user management and authentication features, ensuring modularity and scalability.
